By":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"12個鐘<br />\n啱啱上網試哂咁多種方法都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身上左mojave應該係快左，但你話慢<br />\n有機會hd有野花左裝唔到，你會唔會試下洗機？"},{"pid":"6072bbb8669d2f4e2dfe0987c3446e67e7f64145","tid":874982,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT204904&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fa6650ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204904</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>First</ins><br />\n請開啟 Mac，然後立即在鍵盤按住以下其中一組按鍵。<br />\n<br />\nCommand (⌘)-R<br />\n安裝你的 Mac 安裝過的最新 macOS。<br />\n<br />\nOption-⌘-R<br />\n升級到你的 Mac 兼容的最新 macOS。<br />\n<br />\nShift-Option-⌘-R<br />\n安裝你的 Mac 隨附的 macOS，或最接近且仍有提供的版本。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>Next</ins><br />\n選擇「重新安裝 macOS」"},{"pid":"115a87c7405387c892f256a68c99aef0f7597fae","tid":874982,"uid":31060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"我2012 imac 今日順利更新 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e89f2d2e45403fccb7a668ca0ad2caff6b3e93","tid":874982,"uid":107949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6072bbb8669d2f4e2dfe0987c3446e67e7f64145","tid":874982,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT204904&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fa6650ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204904</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>First</ins><br />\n請開啟 Mac，然後立即在鍵盤按住以下其中一組按鍵。<br />\n<br />\nCommand (⌘)-R<br /